org.apache.flink.streaming.api.operators

类 AbstractUdfStreamOperator<OUT,F extends Function>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.streaming.api.operators.AbstractStreamOperator<OUT>
      • org.apache.flink.streaming.api.operators.AbstractUdfStreamOperator<OUT,F>
  • 类型参数:
    OUT - The output type of the operator
    F - The type of the user function
    所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, KeyContext, OutputTypeConfigurable<OUT>, StreamOperator<OUT>
    直接已知子类:
    AbstractKeyedCEPPatternOperator, AsyncWaitOperator, CoProcessOperator, CoStreamFlatMap, CoStreamMap, ExtractTimestampsOperator, KeyedCoProcessOperator, KeyedProcessOperator, ProcessOperator, StreamFilter, StreamFlatMap, StreamGroupedFold, StreamGroupedReduce, StreamMap, StreamSink, StreamSource, TimestampsAndPeriodicWatermarksOperator, TimestampsAndPunctuatedWatermarksOperator, WindowOperator

    @PublicEvolving
public abstract class AbstractUdfStreamOperator<OUT,F extends Function>
extends AbstractStreamOperator<OUT>
implements OutputTypeConfigurable<OUT>
    This is used as the base class for operators that have a user-defined function. This class handles the opening and closing of the user-defined functions, as part of the operator life cycle.

      • close

        public void close()
           throws java.lang.Exception
        从类复制的说明: AbstractStreamOperator
        This method is called after all records have been added to the operators via the methods OneInputStreamOperator.processElement(StreamRecord), or TwoInputStreamOperator.processElement1(StreamRecord) and TwoInputStreamOperator.processElement2(StreamRecord).

        The method is expected to flush all remaining buffered data. Exceptions during this flushing of buffered should be propagated, in order to cause the operation to be recognized asa failed, because the last data items are not processed properly.

        指定者:
        close 在接口中 StreamOperator<OUT>
        覆盖:
        close 在类中 AbstractStreamOperator<OUT>
        抛出:
        java.lang.Exception - An exception in this method causes the operator to fail.

      • dispose

        public void dispose()
             throws java.lang.Exception
        从类复制的说明: AbstractStreamOperator
        This method is called at the very end of the operator's life, both in the case of a successful completion of the operation, and in the case of a failure and canceling.

        This method is expected to make a thorough effort to release all resources that the operator has acquired.

        指定者:
